Class DatabasePopulator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linqs.psl.database.DatabasePopulator

  • public class DatabasePopulator
extends Object
    A DatabasePopulator can easily commit a large number of RandomVariableAtoms to a database.

    Eric Norris
